1
00:02:12,850 --> 00:02:15,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}Episode 11</font>

2
00:02:17,680 --> 00:02:21,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Guys, do you really think this will work?</font>

3
00:02:21,680 --> 00:02:24,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I gave up a cushy job
to come here, you know!</font>

4
00:02:24,610 --> 00:02:29,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Xiao, just follow orders
from the higher-ups.</font>

5
00:02:29,180 --> 00:02:30,770
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No complaining.</font>

6
00:02:31,790 --> 00:02:33,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">This is obviously a trap.</font>

7
00:02:33,600 --> 00:02:35,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What kind of idiot would fall for it?</font>

8
00:02:35,520 --> 00:02:40,160
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Ha! If you ask me, 
Biyou Village is full of idiots.</font>

9
00:02:40,160 --> 00:02:42,550
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Who do you think came up 
with this terrible idea?</font>

10
00:02:42,550 --> 00:02:44,270
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's not Chairman Zhao's style!</font>

11
00:02:46,170 --> 00:02:47,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Who else could it be?</font>

12
00:02:47,600 --> 00:02:49,930
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Who was closest to Ma back in the village?</font>

13
00:02:49,930 --> 00:02:51,780
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Such an obvious scheme!</font>

14
00:02:51,780 --> 00:02:54,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The Bastard is bullying honest people!</font>

15
00:03:01,890 --> 00:03:03,970
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Father!</font>

16
00:03:03,970 --> 00:03:05,850
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What's wrong, this early in the morning?</font>

17
00:03:07,350 --> 00:03:08,470
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Father!</font>

18
00:03:15,460 --> 00:03:17,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Bai, what happened?</font>

19
00:03:17,750 --> 00:03:20,050
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The Company captured Brother Qing!</font>

20
00:03:20,050 --> 00:03:22,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">They took him to some "secret bunker,"</font>

21
00:03:22,080 --> 00:03:25,100
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">and said they need info on 
a guy called Ma Xianhong.</font>

22
00:03:25,530 --> 00:03:27,050
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Why did you come forward?</font>

23
00:03:27,050 --> 00:03:28,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Aren't you afraid...</font>

24
00:03:28,390 --> 00:03:29,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I feel guilty.</font>

25
00:03:29,680 --> 00:03:32,270
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I don't want to have nightmares anymore.</font>

26
00:03:32,870 --> 00:03:36,430
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I can confirm that they 
really don't know anything.</font>

27
00:03:37,140 --> 00:03:39,770
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I can't bring myself to 
harm these kids any longer.</font>

28
00:03:39,770 --> 00:03:44,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">In five days, if they still 
haven't revealed anything,</font>

29
00:03:44,010 --> 00:03:47,150
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">they'll be crippled and 
permanently imprisoned here.</font>

30
00:03:48,000 --> 00:03:50,720
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I've already told you the 
location of this secret bunker.</font>

31
00:03:51,300 --> 00:03:53,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I want to at least let 
the outside world know</font>

32
00:03:53,600 --> 00:03:55,550
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">what's happening here.</font>

33
00:04:15,270 --> 00:04:16,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What should I ask?</font>

34
00:04:17,270 --> 00:04:19,150
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">How's this guy been doing lately?</font>

35
00:04:30,480 --> 00:04:32,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">This answer isn't even worth reading.</font>

36
00:04:33,990 --> 00:04:36,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The Company really knows 
how to cause trouble.</font>

37
00:04:49,180 --> 00:04:52,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Sir, we have no idea
 what's going on either.</font>

38
00:04:52,930 --> 00:04:56,140
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Look, you were fine for 
the first two days, right?</font>

39
00:04:56,800 --> 00:04:58,770
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">If you don't mind me asking,</font>

40
00:04:58,770 --> 00:05:01,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">why did you flip over our mattress?</font>

41
00:05:02,390 --> 00:05:05,890
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Miss, why are you interrogating me?</font>

42
00:05:15,970 --> 00:05:17,190
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">This is getting ridiculous!</font>

43
00:05:17,190 --> 00:05:19,740
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Day after day! Can't a guy 
get a good night's sleep?</font>

44
00:05:19,740 --> 00:05:20,970
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">How annoying!</font>

45
00:05:21,280 --> 00:05:23,070
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Is this guy crazy?</font>

46
00:05:26,600 --> 00:05:27,970
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Master Wang...</font>

47
00:05:29,950 --> 00:05:30,810
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Sorry.</font>

48
00:05:31,440 --> 00:05:34,390
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Whoa! Finally showing your face, huh!</font>

49
00:05:34,750 --> 00:05:36,890
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You guys have the nerve to say sorry?</font>

50
00:05:36,890 --> 00:05:39,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I've been ignoring you day after day,</font>

51
00:05:39,680 --> 00:05:41,720
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">and you just keep pushing!</font>

52
00:05:41,720 --> 00:05:43,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Have you no shame? When will this end?</font>

53
00:05:45,540 --> 00:05:48,770
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Tell me, what exactly do you want?</font>

54
00:05:49,000 --> 00:05:51,800
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Master Wang, you've repeatedly 
refused Master Kui's invitations,</font>

55
00:05:51,800 --> 00:05:53,140
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">so we have no choice!</font>

56
00:05:53,140 --> 00:05:54,970
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Master Kui told us to follow you,</font>

57
00:05:54,970 --> 00:05:56,780
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">so we can only obey...</font>

58
00:05:57,220 --> 00:05:59,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Chen Jinkui?</font>

59
00:06:02,000 --> 00:06:04,430
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Fine, I'm tired of this too.</font>

60
00:06:04,780 --> 00:06:05,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'll give you a place.</font>

61
00:06:05,830 --> 00:06:06,770
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Tell him to come,</font>

62
00:06:07,280 --> 00:06:08,550
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">alone!</font>

63
00:06:18,720 --> 00:06:24,730
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">There are only three days left 
until the so-called execution day.</font>

64
00:06:28,300 --> 00:06:31,220
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Come to think of it, 
the company really went all out,</font>

65
00:06:31,220 --> 00:06:34,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">giving up an entire secret 
bunker just for Ma Xianhong.</font>

66
00:06:34,520 --> 00:06:36,370
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">How could that be?</font>

67
00:06:36,370 --> 00:06:39,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I heard something happened to the 
Company's first secret bunker</font>

68
00:06:39,040 --> 00:06:40,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">and it was later abandoned.</font>

69
00:06:41,080 --> 00:06:43,300
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">This must be that one.</font>

70
00:06:43,300 --> 00:06:44,930
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Not bad, Zhang Chulan.</font>

71
00:06:44,930 --> 00:06:45,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh?</font>

72
00:06:45,600 --> 00:06:47,850
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">First you toy with that silly girl,</font>

73
00:06:47,850 --> 00:06:50,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">now you've even lured the 
Heavenly Master's disciple to your side.</font>

74
00:06:50,640 --> 00:06:52,700
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hey, Brother Guan Er!</font>

75
00:06:52,700 --> 00:06:54,160
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The way you put it...</font>

76
00:06:54,160 --> 00:06:55,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">"Lure" is such an ugly word.</font>

77
00:06:55,520 --> 00:06:58,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, by the way, Zhang, did you know?</font>

78
00:06:58,060 --> 00:07:00,470
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">They found that baldy, Liu Mingyuan.</font>

79
00:07:02,470 --> 00:07:05,150
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">He was dead. It was suicide.</font>

80
00:07:06,560 --> 00:07:08,160
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We checked with guys in the Northeast,</font>

81
00:07:08,160 --> 00:07:09,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">turns out he was some kind of folk shaman.</font>

82
00:07:09,750 --> 00:07:12,430
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Not very skilled, not famous either.</font>

83
00:07:12,430 --> 00:07:15,200
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">People who knew him didn't 
remember him for his abilities,</font>

84
00:07:15,200 --> 00:07:17,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">but for his unshakable drug addiction.</font>

85
00:07:18,110 --> 00:07:18,980
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What are you thinking about?</font>

86
00:07:18,980 --> 00:07:19,660
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh?</font>

87
00:07:19,660 --> 00:07:25,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Right, tell everyone about how 
you came up with this clever scheme.</font>

88
00:07:25,830 --> 00:07:28,140
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Scheme? Me?</font>

89
00:07:35,120 --> 00:07:36,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Well, it was like this.</font>

90
00:07:36,630 --> 00:07:38,430
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We all had our own tasks back then.</font>

91
00:07:38,430 --> 00:07:40,510
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I was in charge of chatting with Ma,</font>

92
00:07:40,510 --> 00:07:42,470
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">and you guys dealt with him too.</font>

93
00:07:42,470 --> 00:07:43,470
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Describe Ma.</font>

94
00:07:43,470 --> 00:07:45,860
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The kid's got potential.</font>

95
00:07:45,860 --> 00:07:47,970
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">He's just a bit extreme.</font>

96
00:07:47,970 --> 00:07:49,530
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Too stubborn.</font>

97
00:07:49,530 --> 00:07:51,720
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">A brat who thinks too highly of himself.</font>

98
00:07:51,720 --> 00:07:54,350
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Paranoid, arrogant, loves splitting hairs.</font>

99
00:07:54,930 --> 00:07:56,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Thank you.</font>

100
00:07:56,630 --> 00:07:58,800
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I've spent the most time with him,</font>

101
00:07:58,800 --> 00:08:00,890
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">so I've noticed some other things.</font>

102
00:08:01,250 --> 00:08:03,770
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're all right,
but have you noticed that</font>

103
00:08:03,770 --> 00:08:06,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">this guy also has a strong sense 
of justice and responsibility?</font>

104
00:08:06,180 --> 00:08:08,930
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And he has another very important trait:</font>

105
00:08:08,930 --> 00:08:10,320
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">frankness!</font>

106
00:08:10,320 --> 00:08:14,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">These traits of his make me think 
there's a subtle mismatch</font>

107
00:08:14,400 --> 00:08:16,660
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">between him and his rescuer.</font>

108
00:08:18,100 --> 00:08:21,100
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The killer was willing to eliminate 
Company personnel to save him,</font>

109
00:08:21,100 --> 00:08:24,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">which suggests that Ma is 
very important to the killer.</font>

110
00:08:27,720 --> 00:08:30,870
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Ma kept a low profile in Biyou Village,</font>

111
00:08:30,870 --> 00:08:34,930
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">but he welcomed everyone 
without hiding himself.</font>

112
00:08:34,930 --> 00:08:37,590
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">This guy doesn't like hiding.</font>

113
00:08:37,590 --> 00:08:39,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But what about the killer?</font>

114
00:08:39,000 --> 00:08:42,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Ma's close associates and 
his escorts are all dead,</font>

115
00:08:42,710 --> 00:08:44,430
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">which must be for the sake of hiding.</font>

116
00:08:46,060 --> 00:08:47,720
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I see.</font>

117
00:08:47,720 --> 00:08:49,740
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Not hiding versus hiding.</font>

118
00:08:49,740 --> 00:08:53,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're going to exploit this 
to emphasize their differences.</font>

119
00:08:53,940 --> 00:08:57,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So I had the Yaoxing Society and 
Xiaozhan spread the news that</font>

120
00:08:57,380 --> 00:09:01,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">all these people suffered unjust 
persecution because of him.</font>

121
00:09:01,310 --> 00:09:05,280
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I don't believe someone who would 
turn against the Company for Chen Duo</font>

122
00:09:05,280 --> 00:09:07,450
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">would remain indifferent.</font>

123
00:09:07,450 --> 00:09:09,370
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">As soon as he gets this news,</font>

124
00:09:09,370 --> 00:09:11,470
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">he'll definitely make a move.</font>

125
00:09:11,470 --> 00:09:13,770
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">In theory, it makes sense,</font>

126
00:09:13,770 --> 00:09:15,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">but your scheme is too obvious.</font>

127
00:09:15,600 --> 00:09:17,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Would he fall for this?</font>

128
00:09:17,540 --> 00:09:19,220
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And how can you guarantee that</font>

129
00:09:19,220 --> 00:09:21,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">he'll come here once he hears the news?</font>

130
00:09:22,680 --> 00:09:24,720
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">There's a possibility!</font>

131
00:09:25,070 --> 00:09:27,140
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I tampered with the information.</font>

132
00:09:27,140 --> 00:09:28,950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Once Ma receives it,</font>

133
00:09:28,950 --> 00:09:32,140
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">it should be a huge shock to him!</font>

134
00:09:40,060 --> 00:09:41,390
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Someone's coming.</font>

135
00:09:42,100 --> 00:09:45,350
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You didn't actually hit 
the jackpot, did you, kid?</font>

136
00:09:53,770 --> 00:09:55,490
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Why are they here?</font>

137
00:09:56,290 --> 00:10:01,930
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's Master Jiekong and his 
senior disciple, Monk Baowen!</font>

138
00:10:02,890 --> 00:10:05,720
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Master Jiekong, what brings you here?</font>

139
00:10:05,720 --> 00:10:08,810
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're all from the Company, right?</font>

140
00:10:08,810 --> 00:10:12,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Don't you all know why I'm here?</font>

141
00:10:12,060 --> 00:10:14,150
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">With your years of experience,</font>

142
00:10:14,150 --> 00:10:16,270
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">can't you see through the tricks here?</font>

143
00:10:18,140 --> 00:10:23,140
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Although Chairman Zhao has already
explained that this is a fabrication,</font>

144
00:10:23,140 --> 00:10:26,390
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I was still worried</font>

145
00:10:26,390 --> 00:10:30,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">and had to come and see for myself.</font>

146
00:10:31,680 --> 00:10:34,430
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're just afraid 
Chairman Zhao was fooling you.</font>

147
00:10:34,430 --> 00:10:36,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What kind of reputation 
does our Company have?</font>

148
00:10:37,100 --> 00:10:38,440
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Who's the old monk?</font>

149
00:10:38,440 --> 00:10:39,970
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You don't even know who he is?</font>

150
00:10:40,270 --> 00:10:42,720
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">One of the Ten Elders, Master Jiekong.</font>

151
00:10:42,990 --> 00:10:46,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">He hails from Shaolin and later 
became the abbot of Lingyin Temple.</font>

152
00:10:47,030 --> 00:10:50,470
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Master said he was once a 
formidable warrior monk,</font>

153
00:10:50,470 --> 00:10:54,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">though for some reason, 
all his skills were crippled.</font>

154
00:10:54,060 --> 00:10:56,190
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Master, if you're worried,</font>

155
00:10:56,190 --> 00:10:58,200
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">shall I take you inside for a look around?</font>

156
00:10:58,890 --> 00:11:00,190
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Much obliged.</font>

157
00:11:00,890 --> 00:11:04,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Who is this murderous-looking 
Master Baowen targeting?</font>

158
00:11:04,960 --> 00:11:07,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Or have we been disrespectful in some way?</font>

159
00:11:08,880 --> 00:11:09,810
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Baowen!</font>

160
00:11:10,270 --> 00:11:14,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Master, seeing this beast...</font>

161
00:11:14,650 --> 00:11:16,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I can't help myself!</font>

162
00:11:17,020 --> 00:11:19,930
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Master, you're still so full of vigor?</font>

163
00:11:24,450 --> 00:11:26,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Xiao Zizai!</font>

164
00:11:26,180 --> 00:11:28,270
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Brother! Long time no see!</font>

165
00:11:30,570 --> 00:11:31,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Master!</font>

166
00:11:31,560 --> 00:11:33,490
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Where is justice?</font>

167
00:11:33,490 --> 00:11:35,470
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">A disciple strikes his master!</font>

168
00:11:34,690 --> 00:11:35,470
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Master!</font>

169
00:11:36,170 --> 00:11:38,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Master! I wasn't paying attention!</font>

170
00:11:38,250 --> 00:11:40,990
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">My life is so miserable!</font>

171
00:11:40,990 --> 00:11:43,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We all take on disciples,</font>

172
00:11:43,210 --> 00:11:46,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">but look at Zhang Zhiwei's disciples.</font>

173
00:11:46,090 --> 00:11:48,980
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Including the late Master Liang,</font>

174
00:11:48,980 --> 00:11:51,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">each of his ten
disciples outshines the last.</font>

175
00:11:51,960 --> 00:11:55,110
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, right, now it should be nine.</font>

176
00:11:56,220 --> 00:11:59,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And now look at you bunch of miscreants.</font>

177
00:11:59,080 --> 00:12:00,840
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Master! It was my mistake...</font>

178
00:12:00,840 --> 00:12:03,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I... I won't fight anymore!</font>

179
00:12:03,180 --> 00:12:07,700
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The way you are now, 
how are you any different from Baojing?</font>

180
00:12:03,180 --> 00:12:06,650
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}Master, shall we go inside
and take a look?</font>

181
00:12:07,700 --> 00:12:09,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Okay, let's go.</font>

182
00:12:13,040 --> 00:12:15,870
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You see, Master? 
I didn't deceive you, did I?</font>

183
00:12:15,870 --> 00:12:17,890
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">This place is abandoned. 
There's nothing here.</font>

184
00:12:18,470 --> 00:12:21,590
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Ah, this puts my mind at ease.</font>

185
00:12:21,590 --> 00:12:24,140
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The Company must have its reasons.</font>

186
00:12:24,140 --> 00:12:26,550
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I was just being meddlesome.</font>

187
00:12:27,460 --> 00:12:29,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No problem! No problem!</font>

188
00:12:31,530 --> 00:12:33,770
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We'll take our leave now.</font>

189
00:12:34,680 --> 00:12:39,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Baojing, have you kept our agreement?</font>

190
00:12:39,250 --> 00:12:39,970
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yes.</font>

191
00:12:40,470 --> 00:12:42,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Self-defense and exorcising demons.</font>

192
00:12:42,500 --> 00:12:45,390
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Beyond that, I haven't
killed anyone since.</font>

193
00:12:45,840 --> 00:12:48,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Well, that's very good.</font>

194
00:12:48,000 --> 00:12:50,850
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But my inner demons have 
never truly gone away.</font>

195
00:12:52,100 --> 00:12:57,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Master, I'm afraid that 
one day I'll still lose control</font>

196
00:12:57,020 --> 00:12:59,350
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">and harm innocent people.</font>

197
00:13:01,120 --> 00:13:04,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">As long as you haven't given up 
on yourself, that's what matters.</font>

198
00:13:04,790 --> 00:13:09,990
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Remember, if one day you truly 
succumb to your inner demons,</font>

199
00:13:09,990 --> 00:13:12,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">and intend to slaughter the innocent,</font>

200
00:13:13,410 --> 00:13:14,980
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">kill me!</font>

201
00:13:19,720 --> 00:13:21,910
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I will remember.</font>

202
00:13:29,280 --> 00:13:30,100
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Chulan!</font>

203
00:13:30,100 --> 00:13:30,940
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yes?</font>

204
00:13:30,940 --> 00:13:34,150
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Those two kids wandering in 
the mountains since yesterday,</font>

205
00:13:34,150 --> 00:13:35,350
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">are we really going to ignore them?</font>

206
00:13:35,350 --> 00:13:38,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No need, there's no need for 
you to get involved, Xiao.</font>

207
00:13:38,210 --> 00:13:40,350
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Ignore them.
They won't cause us any trouble.</font>

208
00:13:42,450 --> 00:13:44,720
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Brother, Zhang Chulan's trip this time</font>

209
00:13:44,720 --> 00:13:47,050
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">doesn't seem related to finding 
clues about Wu Gensheng.</font>

210
00:13:47,050 --> 00:13:48,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Should we keep watching?</font>

211
00:13:48,940 --> 00:13:52,150
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Let's stay and see what actually happens.</font>

212
00:13:52,150 --> 00:13:54,350
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Today is the Company's 
so-called execution day.</font>

213
00:13:54,700 --> 00:13:57,660
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm also curious about 
what the Company is up to.</font>

214
00:14:02,100 --> 00:14:04,430
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The execution day has passed.</font>

215
00:14:04,430 --> 00:14:06,220
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">In the end, he didn't come.</font>

216
00:14:06,560 --> 00:14:08,270
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No matter how stupid Ma Xianhong is,</font>

217
00:14:08,270 --> 00:14:10,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">he wouldn't fall for a trap like this.</font>

218
00:14:10,560 --> 00:14:11,930
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Thanks to this mission,</font>

219
00:14:11,930 --> 00:14:14,270
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">we've had a few days of peace.</font>

220
00:14:14,270 --> 00:14:16,720
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Still, thanks to you, Bastard.</font>

221
00:14:22,330 --> 00:14:23,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">How's it going?</font>

222
00:14:23,560 --> 00:14:25,430
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I've heard that the Part Timers</font>

223
00:14:25,430 --> 00:14:27,970
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">have all returned to 
their respective regions.</font>

224
00:14:27,970 --> 00:14:29,530
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Is it reliable?</font>

225
00:14:29,530 --> 00:14:30,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I can't confirm it,</font>

226
00:14:30,790 --> 00:14:32,810
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">and I can't dig any deeper.</font>

227
00:14:33,230 --> 00:14:36,810
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's obvious that Zhao suspects 
someone on the board.</font>

228
00:14:36,810 --> 00:14:39,220
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You just need to keep 
watching Ma Xianhong!</font>

229
00:14:44,970 --> 00:14:45,930
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Sister...</font>

230
00:14:46,720 --> 00:14:48,810
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Is this why you made me rest?</font>

231
00:14:53,480 --> 00:14:56,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Sister, do you think I'm an idiot?</font>

232
00:14:56,680 --> 00:14:58,720
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Would I fall for such an obvious trap?</font>

233
00:15:01,270 --> 00:15:02,810
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's good.</font>

234
00:15:10,400 --> 00:15:11,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Xianhong.</font>

235
00:15:12,420 --> 00:15:15,430
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Didn't we agree... 
not to do anything stupid?</font>

236
00:15:17,720 --> 00:15:18,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Sister...</font>

237
00:15:19,310 --> 00:15:20,140
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm sorry.</font>

238
00:15:20,500 --> 00:15:23,930
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I know this is almost certainly a trap.</font>

239
00:15:23,930 --> 00:15:26,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But even if there's a one 
in ten thousand chance...</font>

240
00:15:26,250 --> 00:15:29,100
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">If the Shanggenqi Mutants are 
persecuted because of me,</font>

241
00:15:29,100 --> 00:15:31,480
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I have a duty to seek justice for them!</font>

242
00:15:31,480 --> 00:15:33,470
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">If the Shanggenqi Mutants
 really were harmed,</font>

243
00:15:34,500 --> 00:15:38,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">wouldn't it be better to get revenge on 
the Company after we've achieved our goal?</font>

244
00:15:39,210 --> 00:15:42,050
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Think about why you've worked so 
hard to get where you are today!</font>

245
00:15:42,050 --> 00:15:45,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Once the Cultivation Furnace is complete,
your lost memories can be recovered.</font>

246
00:15:45,390 --> 00:15:47,350
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Think about which is more important!</font>

247
00:15:47,350 --> 00:15:48,390
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Sister...</font>

248
00:15:48,860 --> 00:15:51,930
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">To be honest, I'm a bit disappointed.</font>

249
00:15:52,260 --> 00:15:53,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">After all this time,</font>

250
00:15:53,680 --> 00:15:56,890
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">you still don't know what 
truly matters to me the most.</font>

251
00:15:56,890 --> 00:16:00,810
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">To me, living with peace of 
mind is the most important.</font>

252
00:16:00,810 --> 00:16:03,280
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">If I don't check
on the Shanggenqi Mutants,</font>

253
00:16:03,280 --> 00:16:04,720
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I won't have peace of mind!</font>

254
00:16:06,190 --> 00:16:08,720
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Xianhong, then let me tell you this too.</font>

255
00:16:09,050 --> 00:16:14,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">If you go, you definitely won't find 
the peace of mind you're looking for!</font>

256
00:16:18,080 --> 00:16:20,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Trust me!</font>

257
00:16:20,770 --> 00:16:23,430
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Trust me! You must trust me!</font>

258
00:16:24,250 --> 00:16:28,660
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">In this world, nothing is 
certain except life and death.</font>

259
00:16:28,660 --> 00:16:35,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's trying to understand and judge these 
uncertainties that's causing your unease!</font>

260
00:16:35,020 --> 00:16:36,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Leave it to me.</font>

261
00:16:36,540 --> 00:16:37,970
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Stop judging.</font>

262
00:16:37,970 --> 00:16:39,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Stop thinking.</font>

263
00:16:39,540 --> 00:16:41,140
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Leave it all to me!</font>

264
00:16:41,140 --> 00:16:43,440
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Let me teach you what to do!</font>

265
00:16:43,440 --> 00:16:45,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">This is your path to peace of mind!</font>

266
00:16:46,220 --> 00:16:47,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Sister!</font>

267
00:16:47,520 --> 00:16:53,430
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Did... you know that I've been 
having terrifying thoughts lately?</font>

268
00:16:53,430 --> 00:16:56,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I... I didn't dare tell you.</font>

269
00:16:56,680 --> 00:16:58,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I hate it!</font>

270
00:16:58,180 --> 00:17:01,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I hate these thoughts!</font>

271
00:17:01,520 --> 00:17:04,740
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But they just won't leave my mind!</font>

272
00:17:04,740 --> 00:17:05,360
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh?</font>

273
00:17:05,360 --> 00:17:10,300
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I've been thinking...
 why should I trust you?</font>

274
00:17:10,890 --> 00:17:13,220
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Come on! Tell me!</font>

275
00:17:14,230 --> 00:17:16,720
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Why should I trust you?</font>

276
00:17:31,100 --> 00:17:31,770
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Sister...</font>

277
00:17:32,390 --> 00:17:33,700
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What is this?</font>

278
00:17:33,700 --> 00:17:36,350
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Your hand... is it more than just red?</font>

279
00:19:28,450 --> 00:19:29,220
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Father!</font>

280
00:19:29,570 --> 00:19:32,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Why did you wait until today 
to teach me something this powerful?</font>

281
00:19:32,310 --> 00:19:35,280
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're my son, not my enemy.</font>

282
00:19:35,280 --> 00:19:38,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I hesitated repeatedly 
before teaching you today!</font>

283
00:19:38,700 --> 00:19:41,780
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Do you know how outsiders 
view our Wuhou Clan?</font>

284
00:19:41,780 --> 00:19:42,810
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Mysterious!</font>

285
00:19:42,810 --> 00:19:47,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Not just that, but also 
complicated and flashy!</font>

286
00:19:47,290 --> 00:19:52,350
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Today I'll tell you why our Wuhou 
Clan's cultivation is so complex.</font>

287
00:19:52,650 --> 00:19:55,610
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You talk about learning this and that,</font>

288
00:19:55,610 --> 00:19:58,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">learning one thing after another, 
but when will it ever end?</font>

289
00:19:59,680 --> 00:20:03,840
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Our lives are finite, 
but knowledge is infinite.</i></font>

290
00:20:03,840 --> 00:20:07,270
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Pursuing the infinite with 
the finite is a perilous thing.</i></font>

291
00:20:07,270 --> 00:20:09,260
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We master these arts</font>

292
00:20:09,260 --> 00:20:12,610
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">solely to strengthen our bodies and minds.</font>

293
00:20:12,610 --> 00:20:16,100
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">In the end, we must master ourselves!</font>

294
00:20:17,360 --> 00:20:21,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Its principles and application defy 
the Wuhou Clan's traditional complexity.</font>

295
00:20:21,680 --> 00:20:26,440
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">They're simple, straightforward, 
yet extremely dangerous!</font>

296
00:20:26,440 --> 00:20:27,970
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The spirit of the upper dantian,</font>

297
00:20:27,970 --> 00:20:29,430
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">the energy of the middle dantian,</font>

298
00:20:29,430 --> 00:20:31,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">the essence of the lower dantian.</font>

299
00:20:31,170 --> 00:20:35,120
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Use these Three Treasures
as fuel to ignite!</font>

300
00:20:35,120 --> 00:20:38,470
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Ignite the flame of life itself!</font>

301
00:20:43,280 --> 00:20:47,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You want to use something you 
can't even master to deal with me?</font>

302
00:20:47,180 --> 00:20:50,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Come! If you're so skilled, 
ignite it and show me!</font>

303
00:20:56,770 --> 00:20:59,970
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Impossible. We couldn't 
even succeed together!</font>

304
00:20:59,970 --> 00:21:01,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">How could you possibly ignite it alone?!</font>

305
00:21:05,060 --> 00:21:07,100
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Fortune and misfortune are intertwined.</font>

306
00:21:07,100 --> 00:21:08,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So this is how it works.</font>

307
00:21:08,680 --> 00:21:11,440
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's because those 
ultimate skills were too terrifying</font>

308
00:21:11,440 --> 00:21:14,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">that the excessive reverence for 
the Samadhi Fire had disappeared.</font>

309
00:21:14,520 --> 00:21:18,720
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's because you've become a slave to the
Eight Secret Arts that I've been freed!</font>

310
00:21:28,350 --> 00:21:29,850
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">With your meager cultivation,</font>

311
00:21:29,850 --> 00:21:32,270
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">can you even control the Samadhi Fire?</font>

312
00:21:32,270 --> 00:21:33,890
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Even if you could,</font>

313
00:21:33,890 --> 00:21:35,770
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I roam freely within this inner realm.</font>

314
00:21:35,770 --> 00:21:37,390
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Can you even burn me?</font>

315
00:21:37,790 --> 00:21:41,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hey, am I crazy or are you stupid?</font>

316
00:21:42,180 --> 00:21:45,270
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You haven't forgotten what our 
Samadhi Fire is for, have you?</font>

317
00:21:45,560 --> 00:21:47,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">This fire, fueled by the Three Treasures,</font>

318
00:21:47,680 --> 00:21:50,070
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">doesn't burn firewood or earth or stone.</font>

319
00:21:51,430 --> 00:21:54,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It specifically burns the souls 
of all beings in the world.</font>

320
00:21:54,520 --> 00:21:58,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Run! Run far, run fast.</font>

321
00:21:58,640 --> 00:22:01,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I was planning to burn 
this place down anyway.</font>

322
00:22:01,180 --> 00:22:03,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You bastard!</font>

323
00:22:03,080 --> 00:22:05,720
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">This Samadhi Fire can't even 
compare to the Eight Secret Arts!</font>

324
00:22:05,720 --> 00:22:06,970
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You know that!</font>

325
00:22:06,970 --> 00:22:09,810
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I know. Of course I know.</font>

326
00:22:09,810 --> 00:22:11,720
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's why I can't
 tolerate you any longer!</font>

327
00:22:13,840 --> 00:22:16,430
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Stop! Stop!</font>

328
00:22:16,430 --> 00:22:18,190
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Stop burning!</font>

329
00:22:40,600 --> 00:22:42,970
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Ah, Qing! You're awake.</font>

330
00:22:43,540 --> 00:22:45,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Did you make it through?</font>

331
00:22:58,140 --> 00:22:59,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Zhuge Qing!</font>

332
00:23:00,130 --> 00:23:01,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Zhuge Qing!</font>

333
00:23:02,100 --> 00:23:03,800
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Zhang Chulan has come to the Company.</font>

334
00:23:03,800 --> 00:23:04,970
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">He's looking for you.</font>

335
00:23:05,530 --> 00:23:06,470
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Looking for me?</font>

336
00:23:07,530 --> 00:23:08,850
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's good news.</font>

